item.title: Build an Illustrious Profile
item.dc:creator: admin
item.description:
The powerful combination of having a research paper and a leadership project while still in high-school is a feat made possible by the Impact and Research Fellowship. Sharpen your profile and resume to impress college admission committees, future recruiters and more!

The post Build an Illustrious Profile appeared first on Learn with leaders.
